{
  "stem": "8842.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But what was going on in the streets, that's the worst, the worst that anybody could bear to watch it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "What they did to the kids was very well known because, of course, they didn't bother with them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "If a mother didn't tear-- give the baby away freely, so they let the dogs on that woman.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the dog would tear her apart until she would leave, of course, the baby off her hands.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then they used to take the baby and throw it in.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Just actually throwing it into the trucks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Some of them took the babies by their legs and just beating them through the walls into the truck.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was-- it was-- it was just hard to describe what that was going on there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we lost all our children.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And really, that was-- took apart the people already to the-- to, to the grounds.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "You could never even talk to anybody anymore.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It was-- everybody was torn apart in the most horrible way.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It was in March 1944.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] Politically at this point probably that was much older than I am because I was-- I was-- we understood that something is happening in the world [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] through people that escaped, some of them, the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they brought back news.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Of course, there were partisans also that they ran away from the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And they somehow found a way to come back and, and bring in the news that the Russians are going to back again.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And they're pushing the Germans out from Russia, and they're getting closer to Lithuania, because like Lithuania was in between Russia and Germany.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we-- certain hopes started to get into people's minds.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Maybe we'll somehow survive.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
